data.description: Nicely update, single level living with a 2 car garage on the edge of town.   This well kept home has recently been updated with new flooring, gutters, a new deck, updated appliances, new paint, and an insulated storage shed.  The oversized two car garage has had insulation installed in the ceiling, and partial insulation on the walls.  The property is in excellent condition.  A fully fenced rear yard for dogs, beautiful mature trees in the front, and central air condition complete the package.
